title: Notwithstanding anything contained in the D
clause_text: Notwithstanding anything contained in the D.C. Regulations 30, 32 & 33, the Commissioner may, by special permission, permit fungible compensatory area, not exceeding 35% for residential/, Industrial/Commercial development, over and above admissible FSI/BUA, by charging a premium at the rate of 50% for Residential and 60%for Industrial and Commercial development of ASR (for FSI 1),which is to be shared between MCGM, State Govt. and MSRDC (for Sea Link) in 50%, 30% and 20% respectively.
